@Jorisfournel I am afraid there is something wrong in your network configuration.

The output size is not the same as input size.

You can use a helper function to see the output shape of different layers in the network.

```r
print_inferred_shape <- function(net) {
  slist <- mx.symbol.infer.shape(symbol = net, data = c(168, 168, 1, 2))
  print(slist$out.shapes)
}
```

